            "title": "《大手成交》盈富基金一手約143萬股自動交叉盤,涉3459萬",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社13日專訊》盈富基金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02800:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02800\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02800-HK</a>)於1:56pm錄得1手142.6萬股自動交叉盤,每股造24.26元,較上日收市價低0.8%,涉資3459萬元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　盈富基金現價跌0.8%,報24.26元;成交3.14億股,成交金額76.4億元,主動買沽比率49:51,資金淨主動賣出1.71億元。(rw)</p></section><section><p class=\"\"></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
